					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content"><div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">American baseball pitcher (born 1983)</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
</p>
<div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Baseball player</div>
<table class="infobox ib-baseball-bio vcard"><tbody><tr><th colspan="2" class="infobox-above fn" style="background-color: #002D62; color: #FFFFFF;"><span class="note">Justin Verlander</span></th></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-image"><span class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File/Frameless"><a href="/wiki/File:Justin_Verlander_ready_to_throw_his_pitch,_March_2,_2019_(cropped).jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/60/Justin_Verlander_ready_to_throw_his_pitch%2C_March_2%2C_2019_%28cropped%29.jpg/220px-Justin_Verlander_ready_to_throw_his_pitch%2C_March_2%2C_2019_%28cropped%29.jpg" decoding="async" width="220" height="294" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/60/Justin_Verlander_ready_to_throw_his_pitch%2C_March_2%2C_2019_%28cropped%29.jpg/330px-Justin_Verlander_ready_to_throw_his_pitch%2C_March_2%2C_2019_%28cropped%29.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/60/Justin_Verlander_ready_to_throw_his_pitch%2C_March_2%2C_2019_%28cropped%29.jpg/440px-Justin_Verlander_ready_to_throw_his_pitch%2C_March_2%2C_2019_%28cropped%29.jpg 2x" data-file-width="1816" data-file-height="2423" /></a></span><div class="infobox-caption">Verlander with the <a href="/wiki/Houston_Astros" title="Houston Astros">Houston Astros</a> in 2019</div></td></tr><tr style="background-color: #EB6E1F; color: #000000;"><th colspan="2" class="infobox-header"><span class="note" style="font-weight:bold">Houston Astros – No. 35</span></th></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-full-data"><b><a href="/wiki/Pitcher" title="Pitcher">Pitcher</a></b></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-full-data"><b>Born:</b> <span style="display:none"> (<span class="bday">1983-02-20</span>) </span>February 20, 1983<span class="noprint ForceAgeToShow"> (age&#160;41)</span><br /><a href="/wiki/Manakin_Sabot,_Virginia" title="Manakin Sabot, Virginia">Manakin Sabot, Virginia</a>, U.S.</td></tr><tr><td colsp